metadata.name: Encantadia
metadata.description:
The evolution of art has always been about pushing boundaries and exploring new mediums and techniques.  
 
With the advent of AI, artists are now able to create works that are truly unique and allow for the creation of new and innovative art forms that were not possible or harder to achieve before.  
 
“ENCANTADIA” is a part of my AI Exploration series, which is all about using this exciting new tool to create characters that are unique and mimic my photography style with themes that I love to create.
